svg.title: A map of Wild Cat Island. North points to the right; the island has a teardrop shape with the rounded end to the north (right), and the pointed end to the south (left). The landing place with the beach is in the middle of its east (lower) shore, and the concealed harbour with its Leading Lights at its southern tip (left). The camp is to the northwest of the landing place, and the lookout point is on the north shore.
